# Things the Docker build must not see.
# Keeps the build context small (<5 MB) and avoids leaking dev secrets.

**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/*.log
Spike/
.github/modernize/
.copilot/
DEPLOY.md
README.md
**/README.md
